summary: The diff shows ProxyTab.tsx has been redesigned with a Google-style centered landing layout, a logo with inline 'COLT UI' text, a wide neon-styled search/URL bar with focus glow, quick links, a compact URL bar when active, an iframe for loaded URLs, a status bar, and preservation of existing proxy logic. All REQ-16 acceptance criteria appear to be addressed.

hallucinated_features.description: Quick links section (Wikipedia, GitHub, MDN Docs, HackerNews) displayed on the landing page
hallucinated_features.reason: The build request did not specify quick links or shortcut buttons on the landing layout. This is an addition beyond the specified requirements.
